---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Oriz Universal Converter" description="Privacy for Oriz Universal Converter.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p>Oriz Universal Converter runs entirely in your browser. We do not upload, store, or process your files or text on any server. Anonymous usage analytics (page views only) are collected via Cloudflare Web Analytics in a cookieless mode.</p><p>Sign-in (optional, for premium features) is handled by <a href="https://account.oriz.in/sign-in">account.oriz.in</a>; refer to that domain's privacy policy.</p>
    <p><a href="/">← back to tools</a></p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose { max-width: 60ch; }
  .prose h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
  .prose p { color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
</style>
